'''Axel Garrido Rosenvinge''' (born October 24, 1995) is a Danish businessman. Rosenvinge was born in [[Puerto Cortés]], [[Honduras]]. In the last two years he has achieved a lot of popularity with his revolutionary way of thinking. He has been concentrated in business management. Recently he started a network called Young Business talent to help young entrepreneurs succeed with their companies.

== Biography ==
Axel [[Rosenvinge (noble family)|Rosenvinge]] started a career as a politician at an early age. When he turn sixteen years old he moved to [[Roskilde]], Denmark. After he traveled to Europe and began his studies at EUC SYD Sønderborg in the city of [[Sønderborg]], Denmark, where he studied in the International baccalaureate. One year after he became the president of the study council in the state he lives. He started an education in Aabenraa Statskole (Biotechnology).

